{"tid":642120,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[組隊] 有冇人想一齊籌組一隊 The Boring Community ?","createTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T05:08:01.000Z","uid":106326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cca00e4622b93b7d3d100441b66911ae8d146b91","tid":642120,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"[中二病MODE]<br />\n<br />\n宗旨係一齊去做D 玩樂性高/有趣，但同時又有少少教育/反思意義既事<br />\n出心都係比較個人，最緊要有份做既人享受過程之餘會覺得打破了一些現實生活既常規<br />\n令到自己生活週邊無咁沉悶，甚至發掘到香港/生活既另一面<br />\n<br />\nIDEA其實都係初步構思緊，有興趣既人幫幫手比D意見<br />\n不過係構思之前容我簡單地講述下自己點有會有呢個諗法<br />\n如果大家對TITLE個名好似有D印象的話，無錯，就係源自於佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/213640_d699d88e9c17d829e01426ab4e3910f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F213640_d699d88e9c17d829e01426ab4e3910f3.jpg&h=23eda0ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據痴線佬Elon Musk係其中一場TED TALK所講，一開始既The Boring Company係請左成班intern返黎發白日夢，構思下異想天開既IDEA<br />\n<br />\n點知發白夢發到可以有PRODUCT 熱賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/214001_b62a7d848ae71df1250e6442bf897531.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F214001_b62a7d848ae71df1250e6442bf897531.png&h=c972dd93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至黎緊係歐洲開始挖HYPERLOOP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/214110_8967499658bbf341ac3b097c5b374dd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F214110_8967499658bbf341ac3b097c5b374dd6.jpg&h=5dc985bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一開始用黎發夢既公司黎講，佢地有今時今日既成就真係前無古人後來無者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當中能夠成功既原因當然係Elon Musk一直係背後backup佢地，無論係資金還是聲譽方面<br />\n普通人當然做唔到咁樣既規模，但發夢係每個人都可以做到既事<br />\n而令發夢入面既idea轉變成現實既一個好重要因素就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「行動力」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港真係一個好撚悶既城市，香港人普遍都係好撚悶既群聚，咁一班咁悶既人聚埋一齊又會做到D咩呢？<br />\n希望大家可以一齊發夢，去挑戰下，即使失敗都叫做不枉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[/中二病MODE]"},{"pid":"30d355a676cc3bb611b832fc8271b9d86df98900","tid":642120,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"學術台的人出來喇～"},{"pid":"68afa6bba0939377918f231b4fac66cefe2c368d","tid":642120,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"巴打有無tg 想問下你釀啤酒既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2604282e60d22b852ed49ca45d53c86898e334d2","tid":642120,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:20:15.000Z","msg":"我預計自己50歲就會自殺死，人生已經過了一半，要把握時間做啲on9既野。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 樓主好耐無見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d106e8993b4c6ba2265020e7b5631d2661578b66","tid":642120,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T00:22:12.000Z","msg":"咁即係做乜野？"},{"pid":"c66d7396dcc11da4d6f98469b064d2d89ead5c64","tid":642120,"uid":106568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"有興趣 但冇乜idea住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留個名先"}]}